==========================================================================
Verify fit checks for scalars
---
Foo: {
  date: Date
  int:  Int
  num: Number
}

ok: Foo {
  date: Date "2022-12-12"
  int: Int "123"
  num: Float "123"
}

err: Foo {
  date: Time "12:30:40"
  int: Float "123"
  num: Str "string"
}
---
err | test.err.date | Invalid type for 'test.Foo.date': sys.Time does not fit sys.Date
err | test.err.int  | Invalid type for 'test.Foo.int': sys.Float does not fit sys.Int
err | test.err.num  | Invalid type for 'test.Foo.num': sys.Str does not fit sys.Number
==========================================================================

